  "title": "Construction Manager",
  "description": "<ul><li>Plan, supervise, and coordinate day-to-day site activities to ensure smooth project execution.</li><li>Liaise with clients, consultants, subcontractors, and suppliers.</li><li>Ensure that construction work is carried out according to approved drawings, specifications, and safety regulations.</li><li>Monitor project schedule, manpower, materials, and progress.</li><li>Resolve technical problems and site issues.</li><li>Supervise workers to ensure they perform their tasks properly and safely</li><li>Prepare site reports, progress updates, and other necessary documentation.</li><li>Enforce site safety rules and ensure compliance with workplace safety and health (WSH) regulations.</li><li>Prepare bar-bending schedules if required.</li></ul>",
