    "description": "<p>As a full-service development and construction company, The Cloverton Pte Ltd essentially assists clients from the very outset to the completion of their project. We become partners with our clients in understanding the five basic functions of:<br>\n<br>\nDefining and establishing the scope of the construction project<br>\n<br>\nPre-construction project planning including preparation and scheduling of the projects, phasing plans, budgeting/cost-modeling, subcontractor qualification etc.<br>\n<br>\nOn-site execution of the project includes scheduling, quality control, safety management, subcontractor management, status reporting and change management.<br>\n<br>\nMonitoring and controlling the project<br>\n<br>\nClosing of the project related to the post construction activities</p>",
